                      ~ get_acs(
                        geography = "state",
                        variables = my_variables,
                        state = "CA", 
                        year = .x,
                        survey = "acs1",
                        geometry = FALSE,
                      ),
                      .id = "year") %>% select (-moe) %>% arrange(variable, NAME) %>% print()
